She smiled to Wolveritron. She hugged Chordate's arm a little tighter 
and kissed his neck again. She swayed her hips and waved her tail at 
Wolveritron just incase he was looking. She smiled at Chordate. She 
whispered to him, "So where are we walking to?" She licked the side 
of his neck with her rought tongue.  She noted he tasted good.  In 
case she got hungry, he would make a good meal for her leopard mode.
